'''David Henderson "Dave" Fennoy''' (born [[January 20]], [[1950s|1952]]) is an American voice actor who provided voices for two Star Wars video games, as well as [[General]] [[Pong Krell]] in ''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]''.

==Star Wars filmography==
{{Mediacat|soundcat=Audio files of Dave Fennoy}}
*''[[Star Wars: X-Wing Alliance]]'' &ndash; [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], [[Dunari]]
*[[Star Wars: Episode I Racer|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Racer'']] &ndash; [[Toy Dampner]]
*''[[Star Wars: The Clone Wars]]''
**{{TCW|Darkness on Umbara}} {{C|Pong Krell}}
**{{TCW|The General (episode)}} {{C|Pong Krell}}
**{{TCW|Plan of Dissent}} {{C|Pong Krell}}
**{{TCW|Carnage of Krell}} {{C|Pong Krell}}
*''[[Star Wars Rebels]]''
**''[[Star Wars Rebels: Heroes of Mandalore]]'' {{C|[[Clan Kryze|Kryze]] [[Pilot]], Lead [[Clan Eldar|Eldar]] Warrior, [[Stormtrooper]]}}

